<!--Introduction on how to initially setup an operation. The image should be placed to the right of this texts.-->

<h3>Initial set up</h3>
<ul>
<li>To start open a new window and change the <i>request type</i> to <strong>POST</strong> by clicking <strong>GET</strong> and selecting <strong>POST</strong> from the drop down menu</li>
<li>Click <i>body</i> and change it from form-<strong>data</strong> to <strong>raw</strong>.</li>
<li>Click <i>text</i> and change it to <strong>XML (text/xml)</strong></li>
</ul>

